Title:  Fluidized Sand

Original Airdate:  Wednesday March 05th, 2008 
 
 
Fluidized sand is used to clean high tech tools. By blowing air through a bed of sand it turns into instant quicksand and becomes a crime deterrent. Could it be used as a defensive road barrier and stop a getaway truck?
